title.narrative: U.S.-APEC Technical Assistance to Advance Regional Integration (US-ATAARI)

description.narrative: The purpose of US-ATAARI is to help the APEC Secretariat and APEC member economies eligible for foreign assistance to advance economic integration and achieve the Bogor Goals of free and open trade and investment. The project has two components. Through Component 1, Nathan Associates is supporting APECs ongoing work in trade and investment liberalization, business facilitation, and economic and technical cooperation, as well as activities that accord with U.S. foreign policy priorities. Component 2 will build APEC's institutional capacity for strategic planning and support its work program. The project will produce policy studies, capacity assessments, training assessments, and advise APEC on integration, trade liberalization, and institutional management.
